 * Physical Memory Manager — bitmap allocator, 4 KiB frames.
 *
 * pmm_init_mb2() — call on a Multiboot 2 boot; walks the MB2 tag stream.
 * pmm_init_mb1() — call on a Multiboot 1 (legacy) boot; uses the MB1 struct.
 *
 * The kernel image + heap are reserved automatically via the linker-provided
 * _kernel_start/_kernel_end symbols regardless of which path is taken.
 */

