2	 * Snake — dual-renderer:
3	 *   GOP (MB2/UEFI): full pixel rendering, large board, colored rectangles.
4	 *   VGA (MB1/BIOS): ASCII character grid, 80×25 text mode.
5	 *
6	 * Controls: WASD / arrow keys. P = pause. Q = quit.
7	 * Highscore: /tmp/snake_hi
